Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Get me some Evian!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:33.21,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Go to where they get it from and get me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz342.3\c&H0816CD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(753.6,122.8)}Ma-chan is so mean!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFA1835&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(528,680)}Hama-chan! Go to France to get some Evian Water!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.78\3c&H0816CD&\pos(241.6,86)}Batsu game!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First, He needs to find out where Evian is from!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.61,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(538,589)}Hamada calls the Evian Company
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:47.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Evian Water right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Uhh....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:51.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So I want to go to where you guys get the water from...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:54.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Where exactly is it though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it around Mont Blanc...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Mont Blanc!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna get there on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, Alright! I'll fly there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also get there by boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:10.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah. Alright, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So where is Mont Blanc exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a far place from Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,12 hours on a plane to France
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The alps are here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiming for Mount Blanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada's Trip has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:30.11,On-Screen Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524.8,586.8)\fad(200,200)}Narita International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.18,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,530.8)\fad(200,200)}Hamada is brought forcibly by two managers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You guys are going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you have on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the Batsu game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:44.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean "because"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to fill it up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.63,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's still a little bit in here. This is fine right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A Souvenir!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us a souvenir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, Hamada's plane takes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.45,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,522.8)\fad(200,200)}Hamada's plane to Paris leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What seat are we in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:10.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Economy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Who the hell sat us here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Batsu game, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Suga
