Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.35,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They have Evian here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Look! It's Evian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I should just take this back with me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a Batsu game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Uwahhh!
