Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.95,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We probably still can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.81,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H17F5F3&\3c&H173F8B&\pos(539.2,591.6)}Geneva (Switzerland)
