Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.81,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,584)\c&H17F5F3&\3c&H173F8B&\fad(200,200)}Lake Geneva
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading towards Evian, Hamada gets on a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's get going soon
