Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Are we even heading the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ask the old man.
