Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.98,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(608,590)\fad(300,200)}Are we really headed towards Mont Blanc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
