Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.05,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(336,60.4)\c&H90C5FF&\3c&H173F8B&}Chamonix (France)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:40.61,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(528,583.6)}Hamada joyfully ignoring the Evian task
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, We gotta climb it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's scary! Try looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
