Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so we can spot you out easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I came all the way here now I have to wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading towards Evian! The cable car begins to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.31,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,522.8)\fad(200,200)}The rope cart begins to swing as it reaches its destination altitude at 2000m.
