Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:40.51,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,526)\fad(200,200)}Hamada riding a cable car to his destination 3842m in altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:43.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Uwaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.91,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,587.2)\fad(200,200)}Hamada shaking from fear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.69,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's definitely no water in a place like this
