Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.81,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's on the verge of death isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Right everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's a Batsume... Batsu game
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,BATSUME!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:49.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,From such a cold mountain to this hot place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:50.71,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,524.8)\fad(200,200)}Climbing down from Mont Blanc in search of the Evian Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, It's about an hour away from here.
