Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Enough already. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What?
