Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:20.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! The waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Evian Falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of Evian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is good right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Being so far away from Japan, Hamada finally gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:07.25,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,539.2)\c&H0816CD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(200,200)}Finally, Hamada has gotten some natural Evian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations Hamachan for successfully getting the water from the alps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Batsu game of your Youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dreams are fulfilled with the cool breeze of the Mont Blanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada in good spirits has forgotten the pain he went through to get the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They reach the neighbouring city
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.45,On-Screen Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,585.6)\fad(200,200)}Evian (France)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Come on Suga... Let's go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Evian...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, It's the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:50.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Evian natural spring waters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:55.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They have the Evian water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well we got it from the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it before but the water from the alps is the water from the alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The water that flows from the alps to Evian is then labeled as Evian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So if we just came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We would have got Evian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.19,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you looking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So what's this water!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The water I got from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Waterfall Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,WATERFALL WATER!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If we just came here after getting off the plane we would have done it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It's a Batsu game...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,DAMN YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.25,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,592)\fad(200,200)}A beautiful woman washing her dog with Evian
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Washing her dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"Seems so"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:05.08,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\3c&H4E2594&\pos(240,452.8)}Evian:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:05.08,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an7\pos(288,425.2)}The snow and water from Mont Blanc flows down for over 15 years to the city called Evian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's just getting it from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:08.92,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,519.6)\fad(0,200)}Coincidentally, There are a lot of towns like this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So this is the same water as the Evian in Japan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.91,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This was so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's just water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:30.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:37.38,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(331.2,62)\c&HECA8FF&\3c&H503C79&}32 Hours since the start
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606.4,678)\3c&HFA1835&\fad(200,200)}He's finally gotten the real Evian Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is for real right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is real Evian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the Evian water from the alps
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being an Idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dreams have honestly been fulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:03.25,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.4,63.6)\c&HECA8FF&\3c&H503C79&\fad(200,200)}35 hours since departure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:03.25,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,526.4)\fad(200,200)}Hamada and the crew get on the plane home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.81,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,585.6)\fad(200,200)}Matsumoto is still struggling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.81,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(332.8,58.8)\c&HECA8FF&\3c&H503C79&\fad(200,200)}50 hours since departure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.25,On-Screen Blue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,591.6)\fad(200,200)}Hamada makes it to the Downtown break room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's painful huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,EH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Whats your problem? You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My throat is cleared up though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.01,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Listen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,In Economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You flew in Economy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Just drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's just water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's just water! It's not a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:09.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Alright, Hamada your Batsu game is over with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Not gonna do a competition again.

